parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The malfunction of the airbag system can lead to unintended airbag deployment, which can cause injuries or accidents, or failure to deploy in the event of a crash, which can increase the risk of injury or fatality.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the instrument panel
the airbag fails to deploy in a crash
the diagnostic energy reserve module (DERM) malfunctions.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the seatbelt retractor can cause the seatbelt to malfunction, increasing the risk of injury or death in the event of a sudden stop or accident.
symptoms: The seatbelt fails to retract or release
the seatbelt is stuck or jammed
the seatbelt cannot be pulled out of the retractor
the seatbelt upper harness does not release and attach to the bottom of the belt clasp.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Windshield delamination can cause reduced visibility, which can increase the risk of accidents, especially during rainy or snowy conditions.
symptoms: The windshield appears to be foggy
the windshield has a cracked or shattered appearance
the windshield is separating into layers
the windshield is leaking water or air.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Failure of the front windshield wipers can cause poor visibility during rainy or snowy conditions, increasing the risk of accidents or collisions.
symptoms: The windshield wipers are not moving or are moving slowly
the windshield wipers are leaving streaks or residue on the windshield
the windshield wipers are making a loud noise or vibrating excessively
the windshield wipers are not clearing the windshield properly.
